<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-560-194  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 560 194.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Computers in Banking  August 1989 v6 n8 p54(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Service to offer data of public, private firms. (CompanyIntelligence from Information Access Company) (productannouncement)andM;</TITLE><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Company Intelligence is a new product offered by InformationAccess Company that makes it easy to track companies.andP;  The serviceis scheduled to be available in Oct 1989.andP;  Information on over100,000 American companies is initially available and InformationAccess Company, in Foster City, CA, plans to add an additional2,000 companies monthly.andP;  Company Intelligence is designed foreveryone from private investors to specialists researching anindustry.andP;  Businesses with more than $500,000 in annual sales thatare listed in Ward's Business Directory are included in CompanyIntelligence.andP;  Additionally, Company Intelligence gives the mostrecent mentions of a given firm in the press.andP;  Capsuledescriptions of the ten most recent articles where the company'sname appeared are also included.andP;  Company Intelligence isscheduled to be available through Dialog Information Services.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Ziff Communications Co. Information Access Co. (products).andO;Topic:     On-LineInformation Storage and RetrievalInformation ServicesCompanies.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>